title: Canon Creative 2
description:
Canon Creative Version 2.0 1996

A bundle software containing the following programs(and game):

CreataCard v1
QuiltSOFT
Pattern Maker
Art Gallery/Color Desk
Design Essentials
Curious George Visits The Lake

"Personalize and Print - Personalize and print T-shirts, business cards, and ID badges for business or pleasure -- what you can print is endless.

Look Your Best - Look like a professional with high-quality brochures, stationery, flyers and more.

Certificates... - Show them you're proud with a certificate for a job well done or for a great kid.

...and Frames - Share that pride with a stand-up frame.

Stickers, Labels and More - Show them your style with matching stationery, envelopes, business cards and return address labels.

A Card for Every Occasion - Colorful cards in all shapes and sizes, including pop-up cards, for that special someone."
